Package: tmap
Maintainer: Martijn Tennekes <mtennekes@gmail.com>
License: GPL-3
Title: Thematic Maps
Type: Package
LazyLoad: yes
Author: Martijn Tennekes
Description: Thematic maps are geographical maps in which (statistical)
    variables are represented by visual attributes such as color, size, line
    width, and font size. This package offers a flexible, layer-based, way to
    create all kinds of thematic maps, such as choropleths (also known as
    shading maps) and bubble maps.
Version: 0.6
Date: 2014-06-28
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0)
Imports:
    rgeos,
    grid,
    gridBase,
    sp,
    rgdal,
    classInt,
    RColorBrewer,
    igraph,
    fields,
    vegan
Suggests:
    knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
